We finally have enough evidence to identify the problem. The issue is actually **two separate problems**. 

# Problem 1 (Critical)

Your application contains mixed Jackson versions:

```text
jackson-annotations-2.14.2.jar
jackson-core-2.14.2.jar
jackson-databind-2.14.2.jar

jackson-dataformat-yaml-2.17.2.jar
jackson-datatype-jdk8-2.17.2.jar
jackson-datatype-jsr310-2.17.2.jar
jackson-module-parameter-names-2.17.2.jar
```

This is broken. All Jackson modules must be on the **same version**. 

# Problem 2 (Even More Critical)

This command proved it:

```text
jar tf BOOT-INF/lib/SBINEWPG_2023.jar | grep "com/fasterxml/jackson"
```

Output:

```text
com/fasterxml/jackson/annotation/JsonProperty.class
com/fasterxml/jackson/annotation/JsonFormat.class
...
```

`SBINEWPG_2023.jar` contains its own Jackson annotation classes. 

And this command proved they are old:

```bash
javap -classpath . com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty | grep namespace
```

Inside `SBINEWPG_2023.jar` it returned nothing.

Inside `jackson-annotations-2.14.2.jar` it returned:

```text
public abstract java.lang.String namespace();
```

So:

```text
SBINEWPG_2023.jar
        ↓
old JsonProperty.class loaded
        ↓
jackson-databind calls namespace()
        ↓
NoSuchMethodError
```

This is exactly your runtime error. 

---

# First Fix (Do this immediately)

Undo the Jackson downgrade.

Spring Boot 3.3.3 expects Jackson 2.17.x.

Put everything back to 2.17.2.

Remove:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-core:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.14.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda:2.14.2'
```

and use:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind'
```

or explicitly:

```gradle
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.17.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-core:2.17.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.17.2'
implementation 'com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype:jackson-datatype-joda:2.17.2'
```

