# Permanent Gradle fix

Add this task:

tasks.register('fixSBIJar') {
doLast {
delete("$buildDir/sbi")

```
    copy {
        from(zipTree('libs/SBINEWPG_2023.jar')) {
            exclude 'com/fasterxml/jackson/**'
        }
        into("$buildDir/sbi")
    }

    ant.jar(
            destfile: "$buildDir/libs/SBINEWPG_2023-fixed.jar",
            basedir: "$buildDir/sbi"
    )
}
```

}

Then replace:

```gradle
implementation 'name:SBINEWPG_2023'
```

with:

```gradle
implementation files("$buildDir/libs/SBINEWPG_2023-fixed.jar")
```

and:

```gradle
bootJar.dependsOn fixSBIJar
```

